{"tid":1827834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[手足勸世文] 自編自導自演論的禍害","createTime":"2020-01-17T09:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T13:23:01.000Z","uid":123933,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"515b0e207f2795025ab34ff75c9edd6e8e3d3004","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"每次班狗一捉到有手足有武器，網絡上嘅輿論9成9都係話：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>做戲！老屈！砌生豬肉！</strong></span>咁易入口武器又唔見有狗死！」<br />\n<br />\n最後手足被補，還押，等候審訊。往往上庭時，公眾席係坐唔爆，又無人去送囚車。去到判刑時，呢班講做戲論嘅人又無晒聲出。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>手足往往都成為condom。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n出現呢種輿論，原因有二：<br />\n一：人類鐘意乜都<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>陰謀論</strong></span>，放棄理性思考（我唔係話陰謀論係錯）。<br />\n二：武力接受程度低，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>思想仍然未進入革命階段</strong></span></span>，與手足脫節。<br />\n<br />\n我係呢度懇求大家（我知好多人都無上連登，希望大家可以盡最大努力發放出去），請尊重手足，唔好再用做戲論去抵毀手足嘅一翻心機。<br />\n<br />\n手足要嘅，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>係支持，認同，與鼓勵，唔係要你地係咁講自編自導自演。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n請問下你自己，準備好革命未？<br />\n請問下你自己，咩叫核爆都唔割席？<br />\n請問下你自己，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>點解用你1-2個鐘，去聽審聲援要坐10年或更多嘅手足，都唔得？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有包伏，唔行得太前，兄弟爬山無問題！<br />\n但唔該，言行要一致，亦要與各手足同步心態。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">經歷咗咁多野，你仲覺得<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推返暴政</span></span></strong>純粹靠堅守你嘅低武力原則係足夠嘛？</span><br />\n<br />\n希望各位香港人深思。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路</span></ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"758473110510dfe6f17a6a46e9f58407dbb0727e","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:19:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以廣傳，同埋星期日去遊行。"},{"pid":"65925cf5b7d9d4565a6bb75014fe6fa71d0f26e5","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割，唔係叫你下下都話自編自導自演。"},{"pid":"e7daef19ca7ff8e31ff8b08c9052f5496cf24f3a","tid":1827834,"uid":345989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"119"},{"pid":"48675983838d71f7096b35422289df32d3f5dd22","tid":1827834,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"好似有新名去定義, 叫做認罪師, <br />\n<br />\nbtw 原來法治未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569881cb339928e76fda65e963402185535781f6","tid":1827834,"uid":322962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"fcb43aba9b64600117982786b3da06c97012c4fc","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:23:25.000Z","msg":"幫手俾個正評推推佢"},{"pid":"9581d3e1129e762df0e70bc2672d1c497f83df27","tid":1827834,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:30:46.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"7bbc362597c76514d4290206c7dbdae54928f6b1","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"唔該"},{"pid":"ddb7baf513ddf167486155fed3564c815a61696d","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"3ce249918e85ff79c3a7fe9a4d0d1e2b4714137e","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"出面熱門個po都咁閪多人推<br />\n我講正經野就無人理"},{"pid":"2bb01455e96c3795831f8ada9686d19081ecdb7d","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:40:01.000Z","msg":"推你老母呀"},{"pid":"068ad42cc444f1a14763b29ae5d7d024a70cdf38","tid":1827834,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:43:28.0